site_name: Site of Crayford Town Hall, Library & surrounding land
description: Re-development of the site comprising a 5/6 storey development to provide 186 new residential units comprising 35x1 bed, 93x2 bed and 1x3 bed private housing units with 16x1 bed, 27x2 bed and 14x3 bed affordable housing units and 2,298 square metres of non-residential uses providing a new library, community centre, medical facilities and retail uses. Conversion of the Town Hall Building for use as a restaurant and residential units. The provision of a new civic square, amenity spaces, car parking and pedestrian linkages.
